Description: Zyphor Command Center Web
 A Laravel-based web interface for Zyphor Command Center.
 .
 Provides the graphical management interface used by the
 Zyphor Command Center desktop application, including
 user management, dashboards, release notes, package
 management, analytics, and system configuration pages.
